        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="mx-auto mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900/30 text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
          >
            <BoxIcon name="shield" class="bx-md text-red-600 dark:text-red-400" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Safety First</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Every solution we design prioritizes the safety of occupants and the protection of
            property, ensuring comprehensive fire protection coverage.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div
