          >
            <BoxIcon name="check-shield" class="bx-md" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            Regulatory Compliance
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            We stay current with all fire codes and regulations, ensuring your projects meet or
            exceed all local, state, and federal requirements.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="mx-auto mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
          >
            <BoxIcon name="cog" class="bx-md" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Innovation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            We leverage cutting-edge technology and modern project management tools to streamline
            the entire fire protection process from design to completion.
          </p>
