          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Project Management</h3>
          <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            End-to-end project management with our digital platform that streamlines submissions,
            reviews, and approvals for maximum efficiency.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <BoxIcon name="check" class="mr-2 h-4 w-4 text-green-500" />
              Digital Document Management
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <BoxIcon name="check" class="mr-2 h-4 w-4 text-green-500" />
